OL,5, The co-creator of 1990s US sitcom      
OL,6, Friends has admitted it was "a mistake"
OL,7, not to use the appropriate pronoun for 
OL,8, Chandler's transgender parent.         
OL,10,FMarta Kauffman said she now regrets the
OL,11,Frepresentation of the character, who   
OL,12,Fwas played by Kathleen Turner.         
OL,14,F"We kept referring to her as Chandler's
OL,15,Ffather, even though Chandler's father  
OL,16,Fwas trans," she said.                  
OL,18,F"Pronouns were not yet something that I
OL,19,Funderstood. So we didn't refer to that 
OL,20,Fcharacter as she. That was a mistake." 
